---
title: Moroccan-Spiced Turkey Meatballs in Tomato Sauce with Carrots and Couscous
description: Tender, spiced meatballs, carrots and spinach find a happy home in this robust tomato stew! The secret ingredient in this North African-inspired dish is fig spread; it brings a delicious touch of sweetness. Fluffy, buttery couscous is the perfect side for soaking it all up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-dinde-aux-epices-marocaines-dans-une-sauce-tomate-97659fc3.jpg
